sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant SB as Supabase Auth
    participant DB as Database

    Note over U,DB: User Registration Flow

    U->>FE: Access /auth
    FE->>U: Display auth page with role selector
    
    U->>FE: Click "Register" + Select role
    Note right of U: Roles: Tenant, Merchant, Vendor
    
    FE->>U: Show registration form
    U->>FE: Submit form data
    Note right of U: email, password, full_name,<br/>phone, selected_role
    
    FE->>FE: Validate form data
    FE->>SB: signUp(email, password, metadata)
    
    SB->>DB: INSERT INTO auth.users
    Note right of DB: id (UUID), email,<br/>encrypted_password,<br/>email_confirmed_at: NULL
    
    SB->>DB: TRIGGER: on_auth_user_created()
    
    DB->>DB: INSERT INTO user_roles
    Note right of DB: user_id, role,<br/>created_at
    
    DB->>DB: INSERT INTO profiles
    Note right of DB: user_id, role, full_name,<br/>phone, created_at
    
    alt Role = Merchant
        DB->>DB: INSERT INTO merchants
        Note right of DB: If redirect from plan page, Calculate trial_end_date<br/>based on selected tier:<br/>Basic: +14 days<br/>Pro: +7 days<br/>Enterprise: +3 days
        
        DB->>DB: Set subscription defaults
        Note right of DB: subscription_status: free<br/>verified: false<br/>escrow_balance: 0
        
    else Role = Vendor
        DB->>DB: INSERT INTO vendors
        Note right of DB: verified: false<br/>max_pending_orders: 10<br/>max_order_value: 500000<br/>earnings_balance: 0
        
    else Role = Tenant
        DB->>DB: INSERT INTO tenant
        Note right of DB: two_factor_enabled: false<br/>super_admin: false
    end
    
    DB-->>SB: Profile created successfully
    SB-->>FE: Return auth session + user data
    
    FE->>FE: Store session in localStorage
    FE->>FE: Extract user role from session
    
    FE-->>U: Show success notification
    FE->>U: Redirect to role dashboard
    
    Note over U,DB: Email confirmation sent to user inbox